Sneaker.create(name:"Sean Wotherspoon Air Max 97", price: 700, brand:"Nike", image_url:"https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Nike-Air-Max-1-97-Sean-Wotherspoon-NA/Images/Nike-Air-Max-1-97-Sean-Wotherspoon-NA/Lv2/img01.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1538080256&w=2200", colorway:"LIGHT BLUE FURY/LEMON WAS", description: "Reportedly inspired by Sean’s love for vintage Nike hats from the 1980s, this shoe features both the upper of the Air Max 97 and the sole unit of the Air Max 1, a killer combo. The shoe also has a unique colorful corduroy upper with frayed edges, a truly one-of-a-kind look, with velour from toe to heel. If you’re an Air Max fan, these are a pair that is a must have in your collection and one that will be sure to turn heads. This no accessories version comes with an extra lace set only.")

Sneaker.create(name:"Nike Zoom Rookie Galaxy ", price: 200, brand:"Nike", image_url:"https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Nike-Zoom-Rookie-Galaxy-2019/Images/Nike-Zoom-Rookie-Galaxy-2019/Lv2/img01.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1551049848&w=2200", colorway:"BLACK/BLACK-ACTION RED", description: "This Zoom Rookie sports a multicolor upper with black accents, white Nike “Swoosh”, black midsole, and a translucent sole. These sneakers released in February 2019 and retailed for $220.")

