Sneaker.create(name:"Yeezy Boost 350 V2", price: 600, brand:"Adidas", image_url:"https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Adidas-Yeezy-Boost-350-V2-Core-Black-Red-2017/Images/Adidas-Yeezy-Boost-350-V2-Core-Black-Red-2017/Lv2/img01.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1538080256&w=2200", colorway:"CORE BLACK/CORE BLACK/RED", description: "Known for their iconic collabs, once again Kanye West and adidas had brewed up more sneaker collection heat with the adidas Yeezy Boost 350 Black Red. Showing 'Pirate Black' flashes, these come with a core black upper and sole that has a core red 'SPLY-350' branding on both sides. These released in November 2016 and retailed at $220.")

Sneaker.create(name:"Yeezy 350 Pirate Black", price: 900, brand:"Adidas", image_url:"https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Adidas-Yeezy-Boost-350-Low-Pirate-Black-2016_TruView/Images/Adidas-Yeezy-Boost-350-Low-Pirate-Black-2016_TruView/Lv2/img01.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1538080256&w=2200", colorway:"PIRATE BLACK/PIRATE BLACK-PIRATE BLACK", description: "The first of it's kind and the first Yeezy to hit the main market. These one of kind Yeezys are a collectible for anyone who has not worn them yet. If you call yourself a true Yeezy fan these are a must have in your collection.")

Sneaker.create(name:"LV Trainer Sneaker Boot", price: 1500, brand:"Louis Vuitton", image_url:"https://stockx.imgix.net/Louis-Vuitton-LV-Trainer-Sneaker-Boot-High-Black-Grey.png?fit=fill&bg=FFFFFF&w=700&h=500&auto=format,compress&q=90&trim=color&updated_at=1548081350&w=2200", colorway:"BLACK/GREY", description: "Run or climb your way to the top of the ladder with these puppies. Show off how much your feet are worth protecting. Let every one know that you're a hot shot and there's no obstacle that will stand in your way. Grab this pair exclusively at HypeStore")

Sneaker.create(name:"Public Enemy Sk8", price: 500, brand:"Vans", image_url:"https://stockx.imgix.net/Vans-Sk8-Hi-Supreme-Public-Enemy-Black-White.png?fit=fill&bg=FFFFFF&w=700&h=500&auto=format,compress&q=90&trim=color&updated_at=1538080256&w=2200", colorway:"BLACK/WHITE", description: "This 2006 collaboration between Supreme and Vans was inspired by hip-hop group Public Enemy. The Sk8-Hi Sl ‘Supreme Public Enemy’ features a black canvas upper with Public Enemy’s crosshair logo on the side panel bisected by a black leather jazz-stripe. The high-top’s white vulcanized midsole also comes branded with ‘It Takes A Nation of Millions to Hold Us Back,’ the title of the group’s second studio album.")

Sneaker.create(name:"Supreme Skull Pile", price: 300, brand:"Vans", image_url:"https://stockx-360.imgix.net/vans-sk8-hi-supreme-skull-pile-green_TruView/Images/vans-sk8-hi-supreme-skull-pile-green_TruView/Lv2/img01.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1554255027&w=2200", colorway:"BLACK/GREEN", description: "The Vans Sk8-Hi Supreme Skull Pile Green is a must own pair If you gotta stay fly-y-y-y, y-y, y-y, y. Made in collaboration with Supreme as part of a larger “Skull Pile” Pack, these Vans draw inspiration from Three 6 Mafia’s Juicy J and his infamous green skull tee look from the Stay Fly video. One of three colorways that dropped alongside each other, this pair comes in black and true white, and sports a classic black/white color scheme with a green “skull pile” graphic throughout. Originally dropping in March of 2018, these are a must own for anyone looking to tear da club up.")

Sneaker.create(name:"SB Blazer Frog", price: 240, brand:"Nike", image_url:"https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Nike-SB-Blazer-Frog-Skateboards/Images/Nike-SB-Blazer-Frog-Skateboards/Lv2/img01.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1554254260&w=2200", colorway:"LIGHT LIQUID LIME/LAWN-WHITE", description: "If you're feeling froggy then you should cop the Nike SB Blazer Frog Skateboards. This SB Blazer comes with a green upper, green frog, green Nike “Swoosh”, white midsole, and a white sole. These sneakers released in March 2019 and retailed for $95.")
